text: The Nokia 7650 is a mobile phone that was developed by Nokia Corporation. It was announced on 19 November 2001. It was notable for being Nokia's first mobile phone with a built-in digital camera. == Related pages == * Nokia 6300 * Nokia 3310 * Nokia 6700 classic ==References== Category:Nokia mobile phones Category:Mobile phones introduced in the 2000s
